      <title>Tile 蓝牙追踪器所有者在美国 IPO 后股价下跌 3.7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/tile-bluetooth-tracker-owner-s-shares-fall-3-7-after-us-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蓝牙追踪设备品牌 Tile 的所有者 Life360 Inc. 的股价下跌了 3.7%，此前该公司及其部分股东在美国首次公开募股中筹集了 1.553 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/tile-bluetooth-tracker-owner-s-shares-fall-3-7-after-us-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 星际飞船降落在印度洋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-06/spacex-starship-mostly-survives-landing-in-indian-ocean-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SpaceX 星舰从德克萨斯州升空，然后返回地球并降落在印度洋。这是伊隆·马斯克的巨型火箭第四次试飞。彭博社的 Ed Ludlow 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-06/spacex-starship-mostly-survives-landing-in-indian-ocean-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:29:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软和英伟达将因人工智能举措面临美国反垄断调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/microsoft-nvidia-to-face-us-antitrust-probes-over-moves-in-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国两家反垄断机构已同意划分人工智能行业的职责，授权联邦贸易委员会对微软公司与 OpenAI 的关系展开调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/microsoft-nvidia-to-face-us-antitrust-probes-over-moves-in-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 星际飞船进行第四次试飞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-06/spacex-starship-takes-off-on-fourth-test-flight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SpaceX 的巨型星际飞船火箭进行了第四次重大试飞，这家由埃隆·马斯克领导的公司致力于让该火箭投入使用并为定期太空旅行做好准备。星际飞船和超重型助推器从其位于德克萨斯州的基地发射升空。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-06/spacex-starship-takes-off-on-fourth-test-flight</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lyft 股价上涨，预计三年预订量将增长 15%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/lyft-gives-three-year-outlook-ahead-of-investor-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[来福车公司 (Lyft Inc.) 在周四举行的首个投资者日活动上表示，预计未来三年内总预订量将以年均 15% 左右的复合增长率增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/lyft-gives-three-year-outlook-ahead-of-investor-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:58:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Netflix 进军体育和现场活动，有望重获创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/netflix-record-back-in-sight-on-push-into-sports-and-live-events</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Netflix Inc. 凭借广告支持订阅业务取得成功后，多头押注这家流媒体视频巨头进军现场活动和体育赛事的努力将推动该公司股价下一轮上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/netflix-record-back-in-sight-on-push-into-sports-and-live-events</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 11:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约将扩大与基辅的国防技术和情报共享</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/nato-to-expand-defense-tech-intelligence-sharing-with-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着北约部分成员国解除对基辅发动战争能力的限制，北约计划扩大与乌克兰在国防技术方面的合作，并分享更多有关俄罗斯电子战能力的情报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/nato-to-expand-defense-tech-intelligence-sharing-with-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
